item.title: HTB - Previous
item.description: Overview Web 80 Navigating to http://10.129.242.162 redirects us to previous.htb Redirected to previous.htb Let’s add it to our host file and go back again: Homepage Based on the information on this page, the website seems to make use of middleware. Clicking on “Get Started” presents us with a login form: Login Form The X-Powered-By header indicates that the server is running Next.js: Running Next.js So far we know that: The server is running Next.
